==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: búzài qí wèi, bù móu qí zhèng 

===Etymology===
Literally: A quote from the [[wikipedia:Analects_of_Confucius|Analects of Confucius]].

===Proverb===
'''[[不在]][[其]][[位]]，[[不]][[謀]][[其]][[政]]'''
# If you do not hold the post, do not meddle in the affairs of that post.

===Alternate forms===
[[不在其位，不谋其政]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

